comments: Who doesn\'t Love CSmith :D She\'s so niceeeeeeee. Great morning class, she will brighten your day :D

This is a very fun and helpful professor. The work load is manageable, all you have to do is read short stories, a couple in class essays and a couple major essays. Great and fun class! would recommend it.

Very helpful, sweet. Fun class for anyone who\'s not illiterate. Easygoing classroom setting. Talk about personal stories for daily free writes. Read short stories and discuss them in class. Papers aren\'t ridiculous. Recommend taking her.
